txt.en: You should return to Mablung, who can be found at the Ranger encampment in after-battle Osgiliath.
Enter the culverts and find the Enemy holdout
A large Morgul raiding party is hiding down here
'Good work. You have helped us secure Osgiliath and made safe passage for the Host of the West. I commend your work.'
The raiding party hides in the culverts of after-battle Osgiliath.\n\nYou should defeat the Morgul raiding party.
Search the culverts for the enemy hideout
With the claims of the Variags confirmed, Mablung has asked you to defeat the enemies hiding within the culverts of Osgiliath.
The enemy hideout is in the culverts beneath the ruins of after-battle Osgiliath.\n\nYou should enter the culverts and find the enemy hideout.

'Gladhir has just returned, and confirms that there are enemies hiding in a section of the culverts we had thought to be collapsed. The Variags were true to their word. I suppose it is up to us, then, to honour our half of the deal and let them pass unharmed through North Ithilien. I will send word.\n\n'[placeholder], take to the culverts. Defeat the forces gathered there and make sure they do not have the strength to make trouble for the Host of the West.'
